about:
The tool for slopestyle, hucking, stair gaps, shore riding, urban freeride. Slightly longer wheelbase than the Capital and Suburban for stability at high speed. For 2007 we specified our new NS - custom drawn tubing made from Sanko steel (Japan) that puts more material in the critical areas. The frame is guaranteed for use with double crown forks, and it will take whatever you throw at it.
Suggested setup: slap on a 7" fork, some fat tires and your ready for the most absurd freeride action ever attempted on a hardtail. Warranted for use with all forks up to 180mm travel
